sub_title: Software Developer - Java | Women in Tech
summary:
I recently made an exciting career transition from Industrial Engineering to Software Engineering, driven by my passion for problem-solving and my desire to create innovative solutions.

During my IT education, I've improved my teamwork, communication, and self-motivation skills, while gaining knowledge in programming languages like Java and Kotlin.

I am passionate about seeing how technology can change people’s lives – and I want to be a part of this: improving services or processes gives me a lot of joy.
